# Frontend Development Guidelines

## React Application Structure
The main app entry point is [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx) which renders [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx).

### Key Components
- **Game Component**: [src/components/Game.tsx](mdc:src/components/Game.tsx) - Main game logic with cosmic theme
- **Leaderboard Component**: [src/components/Leaderboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Leaderboard.tsx) - Onchain leaderboard display
- **WalletConnect Component**: [src/components/WalletConnect.tsx](mdc:src/components/WalletConnect.tsx) - Wallet integration

### Custom Hooks
- **useLeaderboard**: [src/hooks/useLeaderboard.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useLeaderboard.ts) - Contract interaction hook using wagmi

## Game Features
- **Character Selection**: Choose from cosmic characters (Smantha, Fake0ne, Frycook, Shitposter)
- **Cosmic Theme**: Space-themed obstacles and animations
- **Score System**: Real-time scoring with power-ups
- **Leaderboard Integration**: Submit scores to Monad testnet

## Styling
- **Global Styles**: [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) - Cosmic background and global styles
- **Component Styles**: [src/styles/Game.css](mdc:src/styles/Game.css) - Game-specific animations and layout
- **Responsive Design**: Works on desktop and mobile devices

## Development Commands
- `npm run dev` - Start development server (localhost:5173)
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run preview` - Preview production build

## Integration Points
- **Farcaster Connect Kit**: For authentication and social features
- **Wagmi**: For wallet connection and contract interaction
- **Viem**: For blockchain interactions
- **Contract Address**: Uses `VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS` environment variable
